---
title: Creamy Truffle and Mushroom Naanizza with Rocket, Balsamic Glaze and Chips
description: Our Creamy Truffle and Mushroom Naanizza is a delicious veggie option that makes it easy to eat more veg in your diet and try something new!
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/HF_Y23_R43_W38_UK_V16162-5_Main_high-3e69f26c.jpg
